###Authentication

POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "admin@example.com",
    "password": "admin123"
}
###Tasks Endpoints
###Create Task

POST http://localhost:3000/tasks
Authorization: Bearer <your-jwt-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "description": "Implement feature X",
    "dueDate": "2024-01-01",
    "assigneeId": "member1",
    "status": "TODO"
}
###Get All Tasks

GET http://localhost:3000/tasks
Authorization: Bearer <your-jwt-token>
###Get Tasks by Assignee

GET http://localhost:3000/tasks/assignee/member1
Authorization: Bearer <your-jwt-token>
###Update Task

PUT http://localhost:3000/tasks/:taskId
Authorization: Bearer <your-jwt-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "description": "Updated description",
    "status": "IN_PROGRESS"
}
###Teams Endpoints
###Create Team

POST http://localhost:3000/teams
Authorization: Bearer <your-jwt-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Development Team",
    "memberIds": ["member1", "member2"]
}
###Get All Teams

GET http://localhost:3000/teams
Authorization: Bearer <your-jwt-token>
###Update Team

PUT http://localhost:3000/teams/:teamId
Authorization: Bearer <your-jwt-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Updated Team Name",
    "memberIds": ["member1", "member2", "member3"]
}
###Add Team Member

POST http://localhost:3000/teams/:teamId/members/:memberId
Authorization: Bearer <your-jwt-token>